properties.Name: FinancialProductType
properties.Description:
A type or classification of Financial Product(s) based upon common characteristics, objectives or financial components:

Ex:
- Cash equivalent
- Stock / Equity
- Stock / High Tech Stock
- Stock / Financial Service Stock
- Bond
- Bond / Government Bond
- Bond / Municipal Bond
- Bond / Junk Bond
- Credit Card
- Payment Card
- Line Of Credit
- Loan
- Fixed-income investment
- Real estate
- Precious metals
- Base Financial Product (ex.: stock, bond, option)
- Building Block Financial Product (ex.: index, weather, season - used for reference or to construction complex financial products)
- Transaction-Oriented Financial Product (ex.: swap, repo - a financial product that is actually implemented as a transaction based on a class of similar or 'template' transaction-oriented financial products.
- Asset Backed Security
- Bankers Acceptance
- CD
- Commercial Paper
- Commodity (ex. precious metals) 
- Currency
- Equity / Stock
- Forward Contract
- Futures Contract
- Mortgage Security
- Mutual Fund
- Fund Share Class
- Option 
- Swaps
- Treasury Security
- Warrant

Columns.Name: FinancialProductTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Financial Product Type.

Columns.Name: FinancialProductTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of a Financial Product Type.

Columns.Name: FinancialProductTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Financial Product Type.
